                    <span>This book has a great approach to teaching C with emphasis on pointers. It is a great resource that will further your knowledge and usage of C language.
<br />
<br />However, the price tag of the book is a classic example of a college instructor writing a book so that they can make it required reading, and profit from their faithful students.
<br />
<br />Ken: The material is on the level, I know your publisher gave you a sweet enough deal to make this book affordable to the average reader.</span>
                  
