<br />
<br />The comparison that is made between them, as well as the use most appropriate of each one is enlightening.  
<br />
<br />The author also carries through a soon however interesting explanation on the design and implementation of ADTs.  At last, the book brings valuable tips and serves as reference for programmers of any level.</span>
                  
